 • neither Foxtel nor Fox Sports would have acquired the AFL pay television rights from either the AFL or News, and Seven would have acquired the pay television rights from the AFL; and
 • Fox Sports would not have acquired the NRL pay television rights from the NRL Partnership (par 225K).

